---
title: Honey-Garlic Pork & Italian Roasted Veggies with Sticky Balsamic Glaze & Pumpkin Seeds
description: The combination of garlic and honey infuses this colourful meal for a flavoursome result that comes together with minimal effort. Top it off with toasted pumpkin seeds and crumbly cheese for a 5-star finish.

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced peeled pumpkin with red kumara, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
